      <li class="responsive-text"><span class="bold">Third-Party Advertisers.</span> We may use third-party advertising companies to serve ads when you visit the Services. These companies may use information about your visits to our Website(s) and other websites that are contained in web cookies and other tracking technologies in order to provide advertisements about goods and services of interest to you.</li>
